{
  "texts": [
    "GANs have made significant advancements in image super-resolution.To the best of our knowledge, [62]used GAN for the first time to detect traffic signs in a traffic scene.",
    "Their proposed perceptual GAN model generates super-resolution features for small objects and uses a discriminator to distinguish between super-resolution features and large object features to provide feedback to the generator.",
    "This improves the accuracy of small traffic sign detection.",
    "[63]introduced a framework containing a generator and two discriminators for synthesizing realistic vehicles in 2019.",
    "This method quickly generates annotated vehicle data samples, which is highly beneficial for training vehicle detectors for traffic scenarios."
  ]
}